  "prompt": "What is the best Android app for listening to and downloading English songs with lyrics?",
  "response": "There are several excellent Android apps that provide a comprehensive experience for listening to and downloading songs while displaying lyrics. Here are some of the best options:\n\n1. **Spotify**: Spotify is one of the most popular music streaming services globally. It offers access to a vast library of songs, including English songs, and has a feature that displays lyrics in real-time for many tracks. It requires a subscription for full access and offline downloads, but it offers a free tier with ads.\n\n2. **Musixmatch**: Musixmatch is a dedicated lyrics app that syncs with various music streaming services like Spotify, Apple Music, and YouTube. It provides lyrics for millions of songs, and you can download lyrics for offline viewing. The app itself doesn't download songs, but it seamlessly integrates with your music player to provide a full experience.\n\n3. **Apple Music**: Apple Music offers a large library of songs and provides lyrics for many tracks. Subscribers can download songs for offline listening. It\u2019s a paid service but highly regarded for its features and vast music catalog.\n\n4. **YouTube Music**: YouTube Music is a powerful app for streaming music videos and songs. It offers a subscription service that allows offline downloads and access to a large collection of music. Lyrics can often be found in the description or within the music videos, and some tracks have embedded lyrics.\n\n5. **Amazon Music**: Amazon Music provides streaming and downloading capabilities for English songs. Many songs come with synchronized lyrics, and with a Prime or Amazon Music Unlimited subscription, you can download songs for offline listening.\n\n6. **SoundHound**: SoundHound is known for its music recognition capabilities but it also includes a music player with lyrics support. You can identify songs, play them, and view the lyrics all within the same app. \n\nEach of these apps has its unique features, and the best choice depends on your specific needs and preferences regarding music catalogs, interface, and additional features.",
